author: KEXP
description: Swedish punk outfit @vboysstockholm return to KEXP with a potent dose of post-punk and art-rock. In a special live session from our Gathering Space, the band leave a room full of fans stunned with a ripping performance of "Man Made of Meat" and more across their discography.
title: Viagra Boys perform "Man Made of Meat" & more Live on KEXP

author: KEXP
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Viagra Boys performing live in the KEXP gathering space. Recorded September 13, 2025.

Songs:
Man Made Of Meat 01:09
Slow Learner 05:08
Waterboy 09:03
Troglodyte 12:23
Pyramid Of Health 16:15
The Bog Body 20:33
Uno II 24:12
Sports 26:58

Sebastian Murphy - Vocals
Tor Sjödén - Drums, vocals
Henrik Höckert - Bass
Elias Jungqvist - Keys, vocals
Anton Toorell - Guitar
Oskar Carls - Saxophone, Guitar

Host: Troy Nelson
Audio Engineer: Kevin Suggs, Julian Martlew, Jon Roberts
Guest Audio Engineer: Christoffer Zaksisson
Mastering Engineer: Matt Ogaz

Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Leah Franks, Scott Holpainen, Luke Knecht & Ettie Wahl
Editor: Jim Beckmann
